room_title: Escape room "The Witness" by Panic In The Woods in Nashville
room_address: 2131 Joe Brown Rd, Spring Hill, TN 37174
room_description: While driving down a country road you witness someone dragging a lifeless body into the woods.  You try to call for help but can't get service on your cell.  Coming across a barn down a long gravel drive, you go into it looking for help only to find the killers accomplice.  You have one hour to find your way out before they return because there can be no witnesses!
